Quickstrike:

 

 

Quickstrike stepped forward. "Ya ain't gotta worry 'bout using th' auto-guns," he told Black Arachnia. "'Cause ah quit! Ah'm quitin' Megatron. Ah wanna join here. Ah'm sick an' tired of havin' t' lay on th' ground t' sleep, an' ah hate it out there in th' Wild! I wanna actually have some quarters and uh private spot. Ah wanna come back here." He passed by her and turned his shoulder to look at her.
